data.description: THIS HOME IS ADORABLE!!! 1 level 3 Bed/1 Bath home in the very desirable BAGLEY/CORNER School District. This home features a lg basement w/bonus room/den & room to expand for the future. In the meantime, enjoy crown molding, smoothed ceilings, bathroom vanity w/a beautiful granite counter top laminate & tile flooring throughout. Don't let this WONDERFUL home pass you by!!!
